# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository and on checkout.
# Windows clones default to core.autocrlf=true, which rewrites checked-out
# files to CRLF — that breaks the migration-SQL-parsing tests
# (tests/permission-matrix-roles.test.ts reads the working-tree .sql files)
# and produces noisy whole-file diffs. eol=lf here overrides autocrlf for
# everyone, so the working tree matches the LF-stored blobs.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never normalize or diff as text.
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
*.webp binary
*.svg  text eol=lf
*.pdf  binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf  binary
*.eot  binary
*.otf  binary
*.mp4  binary
*.webm binary
*.zip  binary
*.xlsx binary
*.xls  binary
*.docx binary
